import React from "react"; import NavBar from "../NavBar"; const FAQs = () => { return(

Frequently Asked Questions

Q: What is CityRunner?


A: CityRunner is the Leading online delivery and logistics service company in Africa.

Q: How do I order/ make a delivery?


A: Sign up as a user through this website and log in to your dashboard

Q: Where do you deliver to?


A: At the moment, we only deliver within Lagos and also locations at the outskirts of Lagos such as Mowe, Arepo, Epe etc

Q: How long does it take to deliver


A: All deliveries are made within 24 hours. Also, deliveries are made everyday except Sunday

Q: What's the price for delivery


A: The price varies on the weight and distance. Check the "Prices" page for the exact price. We assure they are the most affordable prices in Lagos

Q: How do I pay for an order/ delivery


A: After you have inputed your order details, you will be able to pay directly online via debit/card or bank transfer

How do I get an account?


Sign up as a user in order to get an account

Who do I contact if I have a problem ordering online or my delivery is delayed/ damaged


Reach out to us at cityrunnerltd@gmail.com or call us at to make a complaint (+234) 809 396 3988

Can I track my delivery


Tracking your orders/ delivery is only available on the mobile apps on iOS and Android which will be released soon.

How do I know if my order is confirmed


You will receive a confirmation email when your order has been made succesfully

How do I access my delivery history


Log in to your CityRunner dashboard and navigate to "delivered" section in the navigation bar.

How do I partner with CityRunner as a business


Fill in the form on the "become a partner page". It can be accessed from the home page or the footer of the website.

How do I become a runner


Submit your deltails to us using the "Sign up Rider" page.

) } export default FAQs;
